data.description: Come take a look at this beautiful, semi detached home in the finest section of Yeadon.  This 3 bed, 1 and a half bath traditional home features a modernized kitchen that includes granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. This property contains an abundance of character such as the original hardwood flooring, a bright and spacious sunroom, along with a timeless stone/brick exterior.  The sellers have completely upgraded the bathroom and have added a custom wardrobe closet in the master bedroom. The basement is fully finished and extremely cozy. Adding an additional living space and room to grow! Property includes a private driveway with an attached, remote powered garage that adds plenty of room for parking.  All appliances are fairly new, being only 6 years old.  Attention buyers! This property comes with a fantastic opportunity! The seller is offering a 2/1 buy down to assist you in purchasing this home. Take advantage of this incredible offer and enjoy lower mortgage payments for the first two years. Don't miss out on this amazing deal. Feel free to reach out if you need a lender referral. Owners are also offering a home warranty to the buyer who purchases this property. This home is 10 minutes from the 69th street station and the upper Darby trolley station, All major sports stadiums are just about 15mins away, a brand new Amazon HUB is about 2 miles away, it has close access to downtown Philadelphia, I-95 and the Philadelphia airport. Schedule your showing today!
